## Modification Notice
This version is a modified fork of the original TrailPrint3D (v2.5) by EmGi. Key modifications:
1. Full Chinese UI localization across all interface elements
2. Added "Circle Shape" option to the Shape menu
4. Added customizable base size input (100mm default) with per-shape dimension control

